title: Nuevo Estadio de La Victoria
text:
(Nuevo) Estadio Municipal de La Victoria is a stadium in <a href="Ja%C3%A9n%2C%20Spain">Jaén</a>, <a href="Spain">Spain</a>. It is currently used for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Real%20Ja%C3%A9n%20CF">Real Jaén CF</a>. The stadium holds 12,569 spectators.
The stadium was opened in 2001 after the demolition of the old <a href="Estadio%20de%20la%20Victoria">Estadio de la Victoria</a>.
